-- Ambac rejects Buffett's reinsurance offer: report
-- 
-- Tue Feb 12, 2008 5:51pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/12/us-buffett-bondinsurers-ambac-idUSN1228277920080212

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Ambac Financial Group Inc ABK.N has rejected an offer from billionaire investor Warren Buffett to be part of a plan where his company would reinsure $800 billion in municipal debt covered by the top three bond insurers, CNBC television said on Tuesday. 

 Buffett, the chief executive of Berkshire Hathaway Inc ( BRKa.N ), had told CNBC television earlier in the day that he had extended the offer to MBIA Inc ( MBI.N ), Ambac Financial Group Inc ABK.N and FGIC Corp. (Editing by Leslie Adler)